"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-olympics-diver-gets-massive-penalty-getting-cold-feet-last-minute-21391997\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Moritz Wesemann's hopes of winning a medal in the final of theOlympic3m springboard finalwere effectively ended after he got cold feet.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheGermanneeded a flawless dive at the start of round five in order to haul himself back into contention of a podium finish.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wesemann had opted to attempt a dive incorporating four-and-a-half somersaults, which represented a difficulty rating of 3.8.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, as he prepared for takeoff, the reigning European champion mistimed his approach and retreated to the safety of the start of the board.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999652503282662, \"rank\": 3.380160524003741e-05, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's known as a balk, which is formally known as a re-start,' explained BBC diving commentator Leon Taylor.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9875198850919097, \"rank\": 0.012602591509732168, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Wesemann was coming in on his hurdle step and had no chance of making the dive and decided to stop.'\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To his credit, the 22-year-old quickly regained his composure and completed his dive, albeit in the knowledge he would be penalised for his moment of hesitancy  'He would have been getting sevens if it wasn't for the re-start,' added Taylor, upon confirmation of the two-point punishment Wesemann received from each of the seven judges.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But of course what happens sometimes you have to stop for safety reasons and make the dive.'\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain's Jack\\u00a0Laugher, meanwhile,described a poor third dive as the 'nail in the coffin moment' for his Olympic hopes after finishing seventh.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.844794934846344, \"rank\": 0.1828982099471313, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The four-time Olympic medallist missed the chance to add another to his collection after finishing with just 410.95 points, while Team GB teammate Jordan Houlden made an impact on his Olympic debut, finishing in fifth.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999972002963743, \"rank\": 2.7269117757467973e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Houlden\", \"score\": 0.9999754981168253, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Houlden\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Houlden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Houlden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laugherwas handed a huge blow in the third round when he over-rotated on an inward three-and-a-half somersault, meaning he could only scrape 35.70 points and his medal chances slipped away.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on that moment he said: 'It was the nail in the coffin moment at that point really.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I gave it my everything and really put my all on the line, unfortunately it just did not go well.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I wish at that point I could've pulled out, but I am really happy that I continued on because I am a fantastic athlete and I always see things through, it just wasn't the fairy-tale I wanted it to be.'\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Xie Siyi won the gold medal, while teammate Wang Zongyuan finished with silver and Mexico's Osmar Olvera Ibarra claimed bronze.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6905495260057731, \"rank\": 0.3991302245052955, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xie Siyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Zongyuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\"}, {\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8489966568977128, \"rank\": 0.17723633339691586, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2252, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"score\": 0.6438963487816889, \"rank\": 0.35555555555554375, \"text\": \"Osmar\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\"}, {\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"score\": 0.7634134621016982, \"rank\": 0.3099061610421107, \"text\": \"Olvera\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\"}, {\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Winkow\", \"score\": 0.9999994835992735, \"rank\": 4.0733995147950755e-07, \"text\": \"Ibarra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Winkow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Winkow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics fans slam controversial new sport which starts today: 'Not interested, no thanks'  Arrow